messages.content: Compare Gemini 2.5 pro, Claude 3.7 sonnet thinking, deepseek v3 (new), deepseek-reasoner, o3-mini, in terms of code and logic performance

As of July 4, 2025, here's a comparative analysis of Gemini 2.5 Pro, Claude 3.7 Sonnet, Deepseek V3, Deepseek-Reasoner (R1), and O3-Mini in terms of code and logic performance:

**Gemini 2.5 Pro:**

*   **Coding:** Gemini 2.5 Pro excels at creating visually compelling web apps and agentic code applications, along with code transformation and editing [blog](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFfQWVecBGAhm7XrOLrSo8sywslZg4uIU69-5EYMdEvM2h21U2hWqE4anxhuFm-7W20T9RpOqrALVp8pVVN5PBloYB7V3x65nnW3DuQGYivGjXIvYuGvoaV8XwB9VADUMKysw7a8eO_9J3d6DqSmlxUHsGsoLiWlxMlobe9bGPaqVWsav0ZTjyQiriGxPdDJjpsT0k=). It scores 63.8% on SWE-Bench Verified with a custom agent setup [blog](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFfQWVecBGAhm7XrOLrSo8sywslZg4uIU69-5EYMdEvM2h21U2hWqE4anxhuFm-7W20T9RpOqrALVp8pVVN5PBloYB7V3x65nnW3DuQGYivGjXIvYuGvoaV8XwB9VADUMKysw7a8eO_9J3d6DqSmlxUHsGsoLiWlxMlobe9bGPaqVWsav0ZTjyQiriGxPdDJjpsT0k=]. It is considered better for most day-to-day coding tasks [reddit](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGhDZeFtqVhnY7aPwP-2YdiPURji3mkQkKra7AAPMC-joBcqgzcH4SxTzybdm-Xaz0VMp23PK8od2ugw-UQNeQYE0XSKs7oTdZp164F96pnlzqZVZS55aZmJIgczSwEOWH7-2wH_12ITicelBVnpglK-j7ijZaHUi832z3RBmLqZmkYnF1YnWF9NGE0u2fMmKQRdr52N43At6hFag==1).
*   **Logic/Reasoning:** It exhibits strong reasoning and code capabilities, leading on common coding, math, and science benchmarks [blog](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFfQWVecBGAhm7XrOLrSo8sywslZg4uIU69-5EYMdEvM2h21U2hWqE4anxhuFm-7W20T9RpOqrALVp8pVVN5PBloYB7V3x65nnW3DuQGYivGjXIvYuGvoaV8XwB9VADUMKysw7a8eO_9J3d6DqSmlxUHsGsoLiWlxMlobe9bGPaqVWsav0ZTjyQiriGxPdDJjpsT0k=). It is considered state-of-the-art across a range of benchmarks requiring advanced reasoning [blog](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHE2A2S_M8rzJFRuX631ERsnk3GJmlqjT2JpXUm0Is1C2ELKEl5aNPOoTAfMlB5q0Red-lHAgojGA_yZYUMYqR0fH508CI9M5I0KF-XZ8a2wFibxdet9LB6Ajv7Ve_gzr2BWLT_V8TC43s5GEzB3R2LrjZor8sO--U86cmtIFWHBYUpcwq1PS_-s_LtvvIwsMcu5g==]. It demonstrates strong mathematical reasoning, scoring 92.0% on AIME 2024 and 86.7% on AIME 2025 [dirox](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGhDZeFtqVhnY7aPwP-2YdiPURji3mkQkKra7AAPMC-joBcqgzcH4SxTzybdm-Xaz0VMp23PK8od2ugw-UQNeQYE0XSKs7oTdZp164F96pnlzqZVZS55aZmJIgczSwEOWH7-2wH_12ITicelBVnpglK-j7ijZaHUi832z3RBmLqZmkYnF1YnWF9NGE0u2fMmKQRdr52N43At6hFag==). It achieved 18.8% accuracy on Humanity's Last Exam (HLE) without tool use [dirox](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGhDZeFtqVhnY7aPwP-2YdiPURji3mkQkKra7AAPMC-joBcqgzcH4SxTzybdm-Xaz0VMp23PK8od2ugw-UQNeQYE0XSKs7oTdZp164F96pnlzqZVZS55aZmJIgczSwEOWH7-2wH_12ITicelBVnpglK-j7ijZaHUi832z3RBmLqZmkYnF1YnWF9NGE0u2fMmKQRdr52N43At6hFag==) [blog](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHE2A2S_M8rzJFRuX631ERsnk3GJmlqjT2JpXUm0Is1C2ELKEl5aNPOoTAfMlB5q0Red-lHAgojGA_yZYUMYqR0fH508CI9M5I0KF-XZ8a2wFibxdet9LB6Ajv7Ve_gzr2BWLT_V8TC43s5GEzB3R2LrjZor8sO--U86cmtIFWHBYUpcwq1PS_-s_LtvvIwsMcu5g==).
*   **Strengths:** It is considered a leader for overall performance, ideal for general AI assistance, coding, and research, especially with its large context window and top benchmark scores [getbind](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFSKH5V__vV6jgi4Kph15qy3T6st7-NQhM4tm_Mn6EcX5JkyHeYXumSafIDdHvXOaUq1YbZ4WFg6LbKgYZr7SKGl_ffcvBxXkAfRKWhhQPDFkV8zhddRZphKJiBewPLpH2HBwSDxvligpS9a5hlu8oPk2DQLvd13qUS0I46A5P7VbLsW6dEGMtyxkWvFi8kt2pMxD4XIb9gvTmHuG1Gy9WvipzSKoxgeXwsyuDbNROf3WCNUuk=). It has a colossal one million token context window (with 2 million coming soon) [blog](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFfQWVecBGAhm7XrOLrSo8sywslZg4uIU69-5EYMdEvM2h21U2hWqE4anxhuFm-7W20T9RpOqrALVp8pVVN5PBloYB7V3x65nnW3DuQGYivGjXIvYuGvoaV8XwB9VADUMKysw7a8eO_9J3d6DqSmlxUHsGsoLiWlxMlobe9bGPaqVWsav0ZTjyQiriGxPdDJjpsT0k=) [composio](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHFFQQ41ebMDCSFtKe2h61a54aaYV1hybBwjqFwRKY2YzoMvpjnzdxEC6k1HlGBAB28glFACy5r-04aAtnQrwAKfAwUtSquVI0wMds4i-Fmt6r29xW_Qa4TC6PrEVPf82GiMcyAs2IDkL9w4tSnG8i-DeofdWFxEojdh7ZPtn08Zz4=). It is also noted for its speed and efficiency in generating code [apidog](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEhYOg9C5zc0-NUuOlPD8pSdJKt2OJDyI-SCTgBGLgAccKTWqRsL7SdPr_ojUd6f1O78Uks8aKLVzJOTTE1wz_JfK5nUsPZ-iAkjr2WZDT5VZteSUQKQ1apw8FLcAg_kRbBRriUIrX9cqnKQayMVWmE6QuDtRGrpg==).
*   **Weaknesses:** Some users report occasional bugs like uncompilable code or odd special characters, suggesting a need to double-check its output [apidog](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEhYOg9C5zc0-NUuOlPD8pSdJKt2OJDyI-SCTgBGLgAccKTWqRsL7SdPr_ojUd6f1O78Uks8aKLVzJOTTE1wz_JfK5nUsPZ-iAkjr2WZDT5VZteSUQKQ1apw8FLcAg_kRbBRriUIrX9cqnKQayMVWmE6QuDtRGrpg==).

**Claude 3.7 Sonnet:**

*   **Coding:** Claude 3.7 Sonnet shows a clear advantage in software engineering, with a 62.3% accuracy score in SWE-bench Verified, increasing to 70.3% with a custom scaffold [datacamp](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEyoPe9crLCsw0XkEgD5go5c8WhEOUwf29Ir-Bi0PD3C9YZ8RYGqFqwWn-8S85W2uv6plnQT7hsY1v5d8VD1vMfz_wdWKjZ7aHctzcKDomUOb-6s-qS9tO-ta08se0OcGOP5q3vuLUJ5LrD). It shows particularly strong improvements in coding and front-end web development [anthropic](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGhDZeFtqVhnY7aPwP-2YdiPURji3mkQkKra7AAPMC-joBcqgzcH4SxTzybdm-Xaz0VMp23PK8od2ugw-UQNeQYE0XSKs7oTdZp164F96pnlzqZVZS55aZmJIgczSwEOWH7-2wH_12ITicelBVnpglK-j7ijZaHUi832z3RBmLqZmkYnF1YnWF9NGE0u2fMmKQRdr52N43At6hFag==0).
*   **Logic/Reasoning:** It excels in complex reasoning, with the new extended thinking mode demonstrating step-by-step reasoning processes [cursor-ide](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHukgEXPh01XXx97nHV3zf88mI0xAlRHba11duEtMGSuGX4oV7jBola2MPXQOdYbd8QhtcLG4XU4U6rmWnpg-r6utJZ87qRdLSI0UfaaRSIho22OIolTu-8JQz_JumWESeV3wn5sbhd4o6eq331ACy3V42vCnjpYPp4lBrO). It excels in graduate-level reasoning (GPQA Diamond: 78.2% / 84.8%), multilingual Q&A (MMLU: 86.1%), and instruction following (IFEval: 93.2%) [vellum](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGrdmmS5KjiQ1SuNLjHoTAB4zney28VEn0bLpRMFkiZYIW95F1gKEN6m6_CnR_yxNApF7xR5SBqz5Csqqrv99rst51396u7H8emMGLV1iLIf1MMyGCn1wDvIiE8DjV4p-fc3hb8Plmkdo0RY7_zy-UHpVponJ4F2--XT1sn4gJPxylx). Its reasoning is more nuanced and streamlined compared to Gemini 2.5 Pro [reddit](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGhDZeFtqVhnY7aPwP-2YdiPURji3mkQkKra7AAPMC-joBcqgzcH4SxTzybdm-Xaz0VMp23PK8od2ugw-UQNeQYE0XSKs7oTdZp164F96pnlzqZVZS55aZmJIgczSwEOWH7-2wH_12ITicelBVnpglK-j7ijZaHUi832z3RBmLqZmkYnF1YnWF9NGE0u2fMmKQRdr52N43At6hFag==1).
*   **Strengths:** It is considered ideal for coding and complex problem-solving, particularly in extended mode, making it suitable for software development and detailed analysis tasks [getbind](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFSKH5V__vV6jgi4Kph15qy3T6st7-NQhM4tm_Mn6EcX5JkyHeYXumSafIDdHvXOaUq1YbZ4WFg6LbKgYZr7SKGl_ffcvBxXkAfRKWhhQPDFkV8zhddRZphKJiBewPLpH2HBwSDxvligpS9a5hlu8oPk2DQLvd13qUS0I46A5P7VbLsW6dEGMtyxkWvFi8kt2pMxD4XIb9gvTmHuG1Gy9WvipzSKoxgeXwsyuDbNROf3WCNUuk=). It is also noted for prioritizing precision over speed, breaking down complex logic into clear, actionable steps, making it ideal for tasks requiring accuracy [apidog](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEhYOg9C5zc0-NUuOlPD8pSdJKt2OJDyI-SCTgBGLgAccKTWqRsL7SdPr_ojUd6f1O78Uks8aKLVzJOTTE1wz_JfK5nUsPZ-iAkjr2WZDT5VZteSUQKQ1apw8FLcAg_kRbBRriUIrX9cqnKQayMVWmE6QuDtRGrpg==). It is a strong choice for business and developer use cases due to its agentic coding (SWE-bench: 62.3% / 70.3%) and tool use (TAU-bench: 81.2%) [vellum](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGrdmmS5KjiQ1SuNLjHoTAB4zney28VEn0bLpRMFkiZYIW95F1gKEN6m6_CnR_yxNApF7xR5SBqz5Csqqrv99rst51396u7H8emMGLV1iLIf1MMyGCn1wDvIiE8DjV4p-fc3hb8Plmkdo0RY7_zy-UHpVponJ4F2--XT1sn4gJPxylx). It has an extended thinking mode for deeper reasoning [vellum](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGrdmmS5KjiQ1SuNLjHoTAB4zney28VEn0bLpRMFkiZYIW95F1gKEN6m6_CnR_yxNApF7xR5SBqz5Csqqrv99rst51396u7H8emMGLV1iLIf1MMyGCn1wDvIiE8DjV4p-fc3hb8Plmkdo0RY7_zy-UHpVponJ4F2--XT1sn4gJPxylx).
*   **Weaknesses:** It can be more expensive and slower than other models [cursor-ide](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHukgEXPh01XXx97nHV3zf88mI0xAlRHba11duEtMGSuGX4oV7jBola2MPXQOdYbd8QhtcLG4XU4U6rmWnpg-r6utJZ87qRdLSI0UfaaRSIho22OIolTu-8JQz_JumWESeV3wn5sbhd4o6eq331ACy3V42vCnjpYPp4lBrO) [semianalysis](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFUp-Sl519fDGp7NCeWf-5dmEhh0NwgTS94W0rbsTBKRh1nzf9Vq-O1pYAzcOO_9-tjq-1CHlNHi6_qyfjjUQ0xS8DavoEvhsO69jx_rPbNE8CZZP7-vHlNYsM4lZi-ufVnZPDJdb6kgORNuz1srIyFCI4bP83vOnu1aXeGGIYn).

**Deepseek V3:**

*   **Coding:** DeepSeek-V3 produces accurate solutions across all evaluated prompts with high robustness in structured zero-shot Python code generation for LoRaWAN engineering tasks, matching or exceeding the consistency of GPT-4 and smaller models such as Phi-4 [emergentmind](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGsK9t449dTsBk4Gp2zMQMPmwj5VlE3ksnNeT2dMBFbl13i_Lt8LnhXl-ZN1XTk30QQ0NgL2GoePVP2zFPzB3YrH7-inF1lFF_MARQlQVZT-y9c6SRBwl_ErZ7QjErbY-RklRhq7iu3jEPP).
*   **Logic/Reasoning:** DeepSeek-V3 demonstrates strong reasoning capabilities in logical, mathematical, and code-related tasks [emergentmind](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGsK9t449dTsBk4Gp2zMQMPmwj5VlE3ksnNeT2dMBFbl13i_Lt8LnhXl-ZN1XTk30QQ0NgL2GoePVP2zFPzB3YrH7-inF1lFF_MARQlQVZT-y9c6SRBwl_ErZ7QjErbY-RklRhq7iu3jEPP]. It excels in coherent, content-rich text generation and logical reasoning tasks, making it ideal for chatbots and writing assistants [openxcell](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQE5-ChYNGNGwoBgUmW5Igo-gJaEKCCesf8ksaWHsHI50XlfYCaDwy-s0Dn32tRpyMwHgTzHUx2sXmU9mI32zF1xBVVj2yKWEnR8bldaL9h5ThSAMwgIUn-TWtyTxJ1TwFPIV_7uGgAKUH0JkQ==).
*   **Strengths:** It is a reliable choice for pythonic automation, calculation, and formulaic engineering tasks with minimal prompt engineering, excelling in technical domains and outperforming most competing models in robustness [emergentmind](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGsK9t449dTsBk4Gp2zMQMPmwj5VlE3ksnNeT2dMBFbl13i_Lt8LnhXl-ZN1XTk30QQ0NgL2GoePVP2zFPzB3YrH7-inF1lFF_MARQlQVZT-y9c6SRBwl_ErZ7QjErbY-RklRhq7iu3jEPP). It is also cost-effective [momen](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFos7kRL8KGkFLA2vrJphsQMpwUpxQ0lWpyTsJTSYFME_my3iMXfIh46mWB8d2Qc-fZwgyovXY5SOypSvMNeX_ZYKKTPcvtjzwGHKXqERJZB2-4vF76sWHnjiE42XaGhq19DzEqHC7Rtd_Q00AKTNuVxPk9h8EujjIC1XJQZw==).
*   **Weaknesses:** Its performance in deep relational reasoning is limited relative to enhanced models like DeepSeek-R1 [emergentmind](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGsK9t449dTsBk4Gp2zMQMPmwj5VlE3ksnNeT2dMBFbl13i_Lt8LnhXl-ZN1XTk30QQ0NgL2GoePVP2zFPzB3YrH7-inF1lFF_MARQlQVZT-y9c6SRBwl_ErZ7QjErbY-RklRhq7iu3jEPP). Claude's extended thinking mode gives it an edge in deep reasoning, but V3's performance is impressive for a non-specialized model [getbind](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEUz4lHUT-Pbc_LoPrlce45m5LvMaIdGatKjlq52K41MU-bNuLqYtXCfdaB7wRzWc5qFwWntBOeqVljJN-A7L4eWbF_3PZpC6jN7jWHR3pC2z2KLXivatgUxINkuPbdWAKmwe77p-Dwfi1snjHULLPmPiyvKC4fk_3BfhhoShnXMY856DaFrZWOru3Kxd3qx1Ot-ccfjrFMBJuKfw==).
*   **Details**: Deepseek V3-0324 has 685B MoE parameters and a 641 GB total size in full-precision. It has better code-generation and smarter tool-use capabilities and improved reasoning, thanks to RL training with GRPO. It is open-source under the MIT License [composio](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHudgENaTDd-2sR0-YRRsBvVg8X0oWLvSKwQA7PX2y6HLm0artI5crCV1booPsjzrTowURQ0hsNqCKaGvJqz7VZWmPt5w0RFYq04Jb4-vma8PhzrrLEkuD86ozkVBUmXavV0ZV_tMqOhSuZWrFe0dPeY-7X37Ejyk77aqBHiJlaH5aX5xw3AnIpTewZ-g==).

**Deepseek-Reasoner (DeepSeek R1):**

*   **Coding:** The latest update to DeepSeek-R1 has achieved notable breakthroughs in code generation capabilities [aibase](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFSKH5V__vV6jgi4Kph15qy3T6st7-NQhM4tm_Mn6EcX5JkyHeYXumSafIDdHvXOaUq1YbZ4WFg6LbKgYZr7SKGl_ffcvBxXkAfRKWhhQPDFkV8zhddRZphKJiBewPLpH2HBwSDxvligpS9a5hlu8oPk2DQLvd13qUS0I46A5P7VbLsW6dEGMtyxkWvFi8kt2pMxD4XIb9gvTmHuG1Gy9WvipzSKoxgeXwsyuDbNROf3WCNUuk=0).
*   **Logic/Reasoning:** Designed to deliver GPT-4-level performance, supporting multilingual tasks including code generation, content writing, and smart reasoning [deep-seek](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEbAquUVkl6KysNnV5uQpk0RCxXxV2uaxnAib8-E4P4hFDdQOfnB4y0yiJkB7D_g51p3lsKGt0bDg7MEQIth0nVid8c9SGoUgmF_yN-f8QRf2bu). It is better at deeper reasoning and math [acm](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFXefUUdBGEh1J3fKxzrS0fvB_mKrfqmt9Kz4xofNkT3GDYAUjTKs8cBK70zA_Z_ZI_9KP_HYS48HC1oEoJsqvSOSpnTEgvFd7Ll3MF2Ecq2z0nawM42LBdDdnjEVAG_erOYJkUUUdLulPCrqPv8OOhmI9h8KSDWVXuZBb8Wv7oJ6SfGImU). It matches the performance of ChatGPT-4o [acm](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFXefUUdBGEh1J3fKxzrS0fvB_mKrfqmt9Kz4xofNkT3GDYAUjTKs8cBK70zA_Z_ZI_9KP_HYS48HC1oEoJsqvSOSpnTEgvFd7Ll3MF2Ecq2z0nawM42LBdDdnjEVAG_erOYJkUUUdLulPCrqPv8OOhmI9h8KSDWVXuZBb8Wv7oJ6SfGImU). It excels in solving complex mathematical problems, with a score of 91.6% on the MATH benchmark [apidog](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQF9Q3US0jJ-D6dmrlnws-697Mkdg8VJJ4lTTdSOorg6HI2-H36b_XoBaysgPPAaYqn4B3Rn3eyPzdmubHuIbc1Tbwn_v84HtsBlDSb4vcOtCZLHQ_rWPnKIwQCY2Mb5WrndrrgO8Ftu_A8=).
*   **Strengths:** It is open-source and optimized for speed, context understanding, and real-time interaction [deep-seek](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEbAquUVkl6KysNnV5uQpk0RCxXxV2uaxnAib8-E4P4hFDdQOfnB4y0yiJkB7D_g51p3lsKGt0bDg7MEQIth0nVid8c9SGoUgmF_yN-f8QRf2bu).
